values:
Yeah, it's been a while since I've written anything. Oops.

I've been at my dad's house and his computer is so slow that I barely bother going on it.

Well, I'm at my mom's house now. I should be with my dad though. He's going with my sister to darien lake today, and then to see my newest cousin (she's  2 days old), Jesayda Maria. I  didn't want to drive (or ride in the car) for that long, or sleep over in Buffalo with my relatives. So, I just stayed home with my mom. Lucky me.
I was at google.com and i found this picture. I Liked it and wanted Arielle to show me how to put pics in my live journal, so she did, and here it is:

I like www.neopets.com. They've got fun games when you're bored (so does www.bored.com). And I would know about being bored. I just spent the last hour on a makeover-peoples-pictures typ site. Yeah.........................

But neopets is fun. I have 2 pets, and 2 petpets. Yeah....

Okay, Blah. Blaaaaaaaaaaaaah.

I spent the night at Arielle's house.  We stayed up until 4:00am then, I didn't wake up until 11:00.  It was fun we watched a lot of Degrassi, there was a marothon on, even though the guide said differently.  It was fun. Then at, like, midnight we put on our swimsuits and got in the jacuzzi.  It was fun, but i was, like half asleep. Oh well.

Hi, I'm Emma. This is my first entry. I am spending the night here @ Arielle's. I will be having nachos for dinner, and we will sleep on the couch and talk, probably until 3:00 am again. Yeah! I am in a good mood because my birthday and party are coming up.  I will have lots of people (including Arielle) @ my party. I'll have a lot to talk about after my party. Until then, I shall remain utterly and entirely boring.
